title: Kim Kardashian West shares the first peek inside the massive Wyoming ranch Kanye West just bought for $14 million
text:
Earlier in September, we reported that Kanye West bought a massive Wyoming property worth $14 million.

On September 18, Kim Kardashian West finally gave fans a peek at the compound that her husband has fallen so in love with. With the caption "Wyoming Nights," Kardashian West shared an image of the family (minus baby Psalm) enjoying a sunset dinner against the sweeping backdrop of countryside.

Previously, Kardashian West shared an image of Chicago and North horseback riding with a similarly idyllic backdrop.

In an interview with Jimmy Fallon last week, Kardashian West talked about her trip to the ranch with the family, detailing how isolated the property is and even revealing that the ranch has no electricity, reception, and toilets.

And will the Wests be going west? For now, Kardashian West says the family will not be moving there, though she does envision Wyoming as the ideal vacation spot — "I envision summers, I envision some weekends," she says.

You can watch her interview below.
description: Kanye West recently bought the sprawling property. Now, Kim Kardashian West is sharing the first images of the family visiting their new home.
